one false move is a 1992 american thriller film co-written by billy bob thornton . the film stars thornton alongside bill paxton and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; williams and was directed by carl franklin . the low-budget production was about to be released straight to home video when it was finished , but became popular through word of mouth , convincing the distributor to give the film a theatrical release . film critic gene siskel voted this film as his favorite of 1992 .